Single-Player, Quick Game designed for one player to complete in a few minutes.
Simple Controls – Players navigate using swipe gestures (on touchscreens) or arrow keys (on computers).
Reach Campus Before Time Runs Out – The goal for our team is to drive through obstacles and get to campus before the countdown ends.
Avoid Obstacles – Player(s) must dodge traffic cones, other cars, and closed lanes; hitting obstacles reduces time.
Score & Difficulty System – Players earn points based on time left, and the game becomes harder as they progress.
Pause & Menu Options – The game must have a pause button and menus for starting and ending the game.
No Ads or Offensive Content – The game must be school-appropriate, with no violence, bad language, or interruptions.
